<br />
<br />So i bought a loose FND 2 cart
<br />[img]http://img690.imageshack.us/img690/6080/fotoew.jpg[/img]
<br />
<br />to make a much more easy and clean job i considered to swap the huge sram to a cart like this one (that have two place to fit eprom)
<br />[img]http://img686.imageshack.us/img686/4269/fotovn.jpg[/img]
<br />is that possible?
<br />
<br />boths game are hirom and the final cart would have 4 8megabit m27c801 epromz
<br />2 epromz per side</div>

